Package org.firmata4j.ssd1306

Interface SSD1306Token

public interface SSD1306Token
This class contains set of constants that represent tokens of SSD1306 device protocol (commands and control bytes).
Author:
Oleg Kurbatov <o.v.kurbatov@gmail.com> see https://cdn-shop.adafruit.com/datasheets/SSD1306.pdf
